@node Announces
@section Announces
If the frontend is tuned, the server will announce the currently running service(s) in 
5 Minute intervals or when the stream composition changes.
The originating address has to be correctly specified in the configuration file.
It will default to @samp{192.168.0.3}.
A username may be specified in the configuration file. It defaults to @samp{user}.
A SAP broadcast address may be specified in the configuration file. It defaults to @samp{224.2.127.254}.
A SAP broadcast port may be specified in the configuration file. It defaults to @samp{9875}.
